---
import BlockOffLayout from '../../layouts/BlockOffLayout.astro';
---

<BlockOffLayout
  title="Changelog | Block OFF"
  description="Follow Block OFF product updates, launch notes, and progress on AI comment moderation for YouTube and Instagram."
  canonicalPath="/blockoff/changelog"
>
  <header class="site-header page-header">
    <a class="brand" href="/blockoff" aria-label="Block OFF home"><img src="/blockoff/block-off-logo.png" alt="" /><span>Block OFF</span></a>
    <nav class="main-nav" aria-label="Primary navigation"><a href="/blockoff/#product">Product</a><a href="/blockoff/#how">How it works</a><a href="/blockoff/#dashboard">Dashboard</a><a href="/blockoff/#pricing">Pricing</a></nav>
    <a class="header-cta" href="/blockoff/#pricing">Try now</a>
  </header>
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero"><span class="section-kicker">Changelog</span><h1>Build notes for the Block OFF launch.</h1><p>A public record of product, website, SEO, and MVP progress as Block OFF moves from idea to first users.</p></section>
    <section class="legal-layout">
      <nav class="legal-nav" aria-label="Changelog sections"><a href="#launch-site">Launch site</a><a href="#next">Next</a></nav>
      <div class="changelog-list">
        <article class="changelog-item" id="launch-site"><span class="changelog-date">July 7, 2026</span><h2>Landing page and launch offer</h2><p>Created the first Block OFF landing page with editorial design, animated product visuals, launch pricing, waitlist flow, SEO metadata, and legal/support pages.</p></article>
        <article class="changelog-item" id="next"><span class="changelog-date">Next</span><h2>MVP dashboard planning</h2><p>Next work will define the creator dashboard, connected account flow, moderation rules, quarantine inbox, analytics, and platform API requirements.</p></article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer class="site-footer">
    <a class="brand footer-brand" href="/blockoff" aria-label="Block OFF home"><img src="/blockoff/block-off-logo.png" alt="" /><span>Block OFF</span></a>
    <nav aria-label="Footer navigation"><a href="/blockoff/privacy">Privacy Policy</a><a href="/blockoff/terms">Terms & Conditions</a><a href="/blockoff/returns">Returns & Refunds</a><a href="/blockoff/about">About Us</a><a href="/blockoff/contact">Contact Us</a><a href="/blockoff/support">Support</a><a href="/blockoff/changelog">Changelog</a></nav>
  </footer>
</BlockOffLayout>
